FBIS4-16884 "drsov076_s_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-076 Daily Report 20 Apr 1994 Georgia Police Chief Killed in Shooting Incident Police Chief Killed in Shooting Incident LD2004082994 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network in Georgian 0700 GMT 20 Apr 94 LD2004082994 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network Georgian BFN [Text] Dear, listeners. Another terrible incident took place in Saburtalo Rayon [in central Tbilisi] just a few minutes ago. Police Lieutenant General Gia Gulua, head of the republic's Transport Police Directorate, was riddled with bullets from an automatic weapon. Lt-Gen Gulua was in a car during the incident.
